gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 110, Trail Blazers 92
gameRecap.excerpt: The Rockets with their ninth straight game as they defeat the Trail Blazers, 110-92. Jalen Green led the way for the Rockets with 27 points, six rebounds, three assists and four 3PM, while Jock Landale added 17 points and nine rebounds in the victory. Dalano Banton led all scorers with 28 points, along with 11 rebounds and five assists for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort. The Rockets improve to 36-35 on the season, while the Trail Blazers fall to 19-53.
